</taxonomicName>
) in many localities in 
<collectingCountry box="[771,836,580,605]" name="Malta" pageId="15" pageNumber="514">Malta</collectingCountry>
and probably also in 
<collectingRegion box="[1089,1155,580,605]" country="Malta" name="Zebbug" pageId="15" pageNumber="514">Gozo</collectingRegion>
”. No Maltese specimens have been seen during the present work.
</paragraph>
